%N A286109 Square array read by antidiagonals: A(n,k) = T(n XOR k, 2*(n AND k)), where T(n,k) is sequence A001477 considered as a two-dimensional table, AND is bitwise-and (A004198) and XOR is bitwise-xor (A003987).
